^6 3 d^0 4 s^0-$ no unpaired $\\mathrm{e}^{-}$. $\\mathrm{V}^{3+}(20)=1 s^2 2 s^2 2 p^6 3 s^2 3 p^6 3 d^2 4 s^0$ - Two unpaired $\\mathrm{e}^{-}$. $\\mathrm{Zn}^{2+}(28)=1 s^2 2 s^2 2 p^6 3 s^2 3 p^6 3 d^{10} 4 s^0-$ no unpaired $\\mathrm{e}^{-}$. hence $\\left[\\mathrm{V}\\left(\\mathrm{NH}_3\\right)_6\\right]^{3+}$ will most likely absorb visible light.", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "masterId": "MOGJMPYQ30639474", "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "bucket": "", "isRemoved": false, "cpyqbSubjects": ["615f0cf69476412f48314dac", "616057040283de43c87e3e16", "61bb58281213731910ea0b71", "6160579d0283de43c87e3e1f", "61964f94a5a526011886801e", "61c055f6e8ce0dc8a5c62d34", "61a8a2cce8ce0dc8a5c62d2e", "6160577e0283de43c87e3e1c", "616057210283de43c87e3e19", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352c", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd8", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7e", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625c", "61964ff3a5a5260118868022", "64d50c263df7f4a7f3017f70", "66b79b89d4b564dfab4f94d0", "678ea9a09cc79e5f592bdc12", "67fa602f4468eb1307ceb0ae", "6807d350647479b8e869647a"], "cpyqbChapters": ["616024f4ce21b5cba7c55599", "616024f1f8b97731aafc60d6", "61c089be659d02341fe42bce", "61bb822d28d60409d131ec72", "61e7bd8115b9968c5625dc7d", "616024f22bdae059334a53e7", "616024f42aaf80dacc3609df", "61964cb73dbd768a400b833a", "616024f5e8331606aad107c5", "61964cb58daf8c64cdbf2a5e", "629109dbc567cef438b2a396", "62962117eaeca617c0b0f5e7", "629f38ff57dc3a63489b4490", "629f3a849a338a11d93a1a44", "64eb06cb3118f713ecfef0ea", "66d5853fa75f05ee8564f59a", "67921d711d5b5072da5e9b16", "67fdff3f378e1624ea7b6937", "68091fea3a10446a207fdc3e"], "cpyqbExams": ["615f0e999476412f48314daf", "616059af0283de43c87e3e23"]}}